short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Open multiple URLs in new tabs
short.hi: नए टैब में अनेक URL खोलें

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Open Bulk Url is a browser extension that allows you to open multiple URLs in new tabs.

Helpful when you have a list of URLs that you want to open in new tabs.

Save different lists according to your workflow and open them in new tabs.

## Features

- Open multiple URLs in new tabs
- Save and load lists of URLs
- Clear storage
- Easy to save your favorite list of urls and open them in new tabs

## Permission Explanation

- `tabs`: This permission is required to get the URLs of the tabs that are currently open.
- `storage`: This permission is required to save and load the lists of URLs.
